{"tid":2014521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［唔洗再選主席］李慧琼： 本週五不開內會 27號前會否再開要再決定","createTime":"2020-05-13T05:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T06:17:35.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"35f7f18d64cb0882749f112c6178c7ff9113ae5b","tid":2014521,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T05:47:14.000Z","msg":"李慧琼今早接受《蘋果》查詢時表示，本周五將不會召開內會會議，原因是她希望「（民主派和建制派）大家冷靜一下」，並已邀請建制派「班長」廖長江和民主派會議召集人陳淑莊「傾一傾」。問到本月27日《國歌法》提交立法會大會進行二讀前，她會否再召開內會會議時？她則說：「稍後先做決定」。<br />\n<br />\n詳情 ：<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200513/FPWH2K3WSSY6FAYRQHY3Q5RWUA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200513%2FFPWH2K3WSSY6FAYRQHY3Q5RWUA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=803603cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200513%2FFPWH2K3WSSY6FAYRQHY3Q5RWUA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=b8f709fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200513/FPWH2K3WSSY6FAYRQHY3Q5RWUA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"eaa0a15b808041a0c43aed9c6906c180d8fe6e7d","tid":2014521,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T05:48:05.000Z","msg":"反正永續咗主席，鄰國想幾時上二讀都得，而家緊係HEA做"},{"pid":"5db3160b3a581822a8d54cc671a24bd2d1ab9ff8","tid":2014521,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eaa0a15b808041a0c43aed9c6906c180d8fe6e7d","tid":2014521,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T05:48:05.000Z","msg":"反正永續咗主席，鄰國想幾時上二讀都得